@-Pucko-

1. Download Daemon Tools from http://www.daemon-tools.cc/eng/downloads (Lite version will do)
2. Install
3. Right click on the "Daemon Tools" icon in the notification area
4. Go to "Virtual Devices",then select any1 of the virtual devices & select "Mount Image"
5. Locate the ISO & click "Open". Thats it!!
ENJOY!!!
